# Solana Demo Project Overview

This is a Solana-based project that implements a staking pool system. The project is built using Next.js for the frontend and Solana programs for the blockchain functionality.

## Key Directories

- `src/` - Contains the frontend application code
  - `app/` - Next.js application routes and pages
  - `components/` - Reusable React components
  - `lib/` - Utility functions and shared code

- `programs/` - Contains Solana program code
  - `stake-pool/` - The main staking pool program implementation

- `test-ledger/` - Local test environment for Solana
- `test-wallet.json` - Test wallet configuration

## Important Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts
- [next.config.js](mdc:next.config.js) - Next.js configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
